## Cross-Channel Adaptation Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the core creative: The single strategic idea or message to adapt
- [ ] 2. Map channel requirements: Format, length, aspect ratio, tone for each channel
- [ ] 3. Create adaptations: Transform the core creative for each channel
- [ ] 4. Maintain consistency: Ensure brand voice and key message are preserved
- [ ] 5. Optimize for platform: Use native features, formats, and behaviors
- [ ] 6. Review each adaptation: Does this work for its specific channel?
- [ ] 7. Document all versions: Maintain a master file of all adaptations

## Key Inputs
- Core creative: {{core_creative}}
- Channels: {{channels}}
- Brand guidelines: {{brand_guidelines}}
- Campaign message: {{campaign_message}}
